Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去發傳單了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發傳單到這週為止就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是之前說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那是作為修行的一環 但發傳單原本是使魔的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經不用發傳單了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就需要你們先找到自己的使魔
Comment: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
